span.span: As ordered by the State of Arizona Department of Education, all schools are closed because of the Covid-19 virus. Desert Star Academy will continue to serve our Scholars & Families during this trying time.
Elementary (K-5) and Spartans (6-8) now each have their separate home page. Please use the menu bar OR the click boxes below to get important information for each school level.
Looking forward, enrollment packets for the next school year are now available under PARENT RESOURCES.
Parents that have scholars with an IEP need to complete a Parent Survey. The survey is online. Click >

Desert Star is applying for an after school program grant. If we are awarded this grant, our after school program would be free to all scholars. The program would consist of mandatory tutoring and homework session followed by enrichment activities and field trips.
